{"tid":1821953,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔係兄弟爬山，各有各做咩？做咩為咗元氣呢D小角色鬧交啊？","createTime":"2020-01-12T15:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T15:00:09.000Z","uid":190579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"13c2d13c5e8aec026565a4f904a02e7735a4b78b","tid":1821953,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:52:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span></span></strong></div><br />\n又唔係殺人放火TK，點解要嘈交呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔buy咪用另一個方向做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗小小元氣去嘈真係好唔抵囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為一個左膠和理非 <span style=\"color: red;\"> （-0-0 ) </span> <br />\n就算我唔buy影大頭，我都唔會阻止手足<br />\n我會用自己既方法做<br />\n<br />\n我已準備豪擲<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>50大圓</strong></span>光顧黃色印刷舖大量全彩印制<br />\n向排緊元氣既市民派溫馨提示小傳單<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">傳單圖例：</span></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7mJ.yxFU9w7Vrxt_a9liqA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/025625d8a38086e17f92e831dd1e5ca2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7mJ.yxFU9w7Vrxt_a9liqA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F025625d8a38086e17f92e831dd1e5ca2&h=e7111b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/genki-01_jpoSZ_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fme